data.description: Beautiful custom-built RANCH home ideally located in an established neighborhood across from park.This home is sure to please with nearly 3000 sqft finished, showcasing a vaulted great room, fireplace, maple cabinets and built-in hutch in dining room.  The kitchen is bright and cheery with white cabinets, SS appliances, desk and pantry. The 14 x 13 primary suite features double vanity, bubble tub, & walk-in closet.  The 2 other generous sized bedrooms share a 2nd full bathroom. The finished lower level boasts a roomy 2nd family living/rec space with built-ins, a 4th bedroom, bathroom w/tile shower, a flex space that could be a non-traditional 5th bedroom/office/exercise room, AND an unbelievable theatre room (including equipment)…perfect for family “fun” nights!  There’s more!  Enjoy relaxing on the deck, patio, and firepit in the spacious backyard!  Privacy fence and a shed built on slab with the same grade materials on house. This home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and location with quick access to hwy 415, schools, and Saylorville Lake.  Washer and dryer included.  This home is truly a must-see!
